Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="179345" author="niu" created="Tue, 3 Jan 2017 03:24:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I believe this is dup of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4382&quot; title=&quot;kernel BUG at fs/jbd2/transaction.c:1033&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4382&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4382&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, it reoccurred because of a regression introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6722&quot; title=&quot;sanity-lfsck test_1a: FAIL: (3) Fail to start LFSCK for namespace!&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6722&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6722&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/15334/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/15334/&lt;/a&gt; where we reverted part of the original fix from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4382&quot; title=&quot;kernel BUG at fs/jbd2/transaction.c:1033&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4382&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4382&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; mistakenly. This regression is amended in 2.8 by &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/19732/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/19732/&lt;/a&gt; (this patch is tracked in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6722&quot; title=&quot;sanity-lfsck test_1a: FAIL: (3) Fail to start LFSCK for namespace!&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6722&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6722&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; as well)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
